title: Ep176 Hypnosis Crimes
description: This week, the gals get very, very sleepy as they look into some mystical mishaps. Topics include a beguiling young woman with a questionable defense, a predatory "doctor" and his murderous muse, plus Lucy's attempt at hypnosis. Pour a glass of Winc's Diviner Cabernet Sauvignon, lie back, relax, and tune in for Hypnosis Crimes. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
